					<![CDATA[
						 <p>That video is kind of amazing, the right combination of low production quality, slightly unsettling and constant rambling.</p> <p>Unfortunately, I don't really buy that this is something dado would make. The drugs seem cruel rather than unintentionally incorrect, which seems very out of character for him, especially as it's something so self-serving.</p> 
