						 <p>So this and the tale &quot;<a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/not-my-circus-not-my-monkeys">Not My Circus Not My Monkeys</a>&quot; are my and LordStoneFish's entries for Collab-con2019! LordStoneFish is absent at the moment for unknown reasons, but A Random Day ruled that his contribution was still sufficient to count.</p> <p>I'm also aware that our entries play the 'collaboration' element a little fast and loose, and if that disqualifies them so be it. I just couldn't imagine any collaboration between the Circus and dado ending well.</p> <p>Thanks to everyone who looked these over.</p> 
